profile_summary:
Sanu Muhammed C is a highly accomplished software engineer with a strong proficiency in programming languages, including C, C++, and Python. Boasting an impressive network of 44 followers and a portfolio of 81 public repositories, he has established himself as a reliable and innovative developer. With a solid educational foundation from the esteemed CUSAT, Sanu has developed a unique ability to tackle complex real-world problems with effective technical solutions.

As a driven professional, Sanu takes pride in building cutting-edge technology solutions that drive business growth and efficiency. His expertise in software development is complemented by his passion for entrepreneurship, having co-founded a startup that showcases his innovative spirit and leadership skills. With a keen focus on delivering high-quality solutions, Sanu has positioned himself as a go-to expert in his field, offering a unique blend of technical expertise, entrepreneurial drive, and an unwavering commitment to solving real-world problems.
